# Email Configuration
# Gmail SMTP Settings
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace your-email@gmail.com with your Gmail address
# 3. Replace your-app-password with your Gmail App Password
# 
# To get Gmail App Password:
# 1. Go to Google Account settings
# 2. Security → 2-Step Verification (enable if not already)
# 3. App passwords → Generate app password
# 4. Use the generated password here
#
# Note: Never use your regular Gmail password for security reasons